  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare CO values obtained by the lithium indicator dilution method and pulse power
      analysis before, during and after anaesthesia and surgery for the elective repair of
      abdominal aortic aneurysms. This will enable us to determine how often and when calibration
      of the pulse power analysis derived CO is required.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
