    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients presenting for elective abdominal aortic and extent 4 thoracoabdominal aortic
             aneurysm repair

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients not giving informed consent.

          -  Patients under the age of 18 years.

          -  Patients who may be pregnant

          -  Patients with learning disabilities.

          -  Rhythm other than sinus rhythm.

          -  Patients on oral lithium therapy.

          -  Patients less than 40kg

          -  Patients with severe mitral regurgitation
      </textblock>
